OL,5, A sculpture mocking Spain's former King
OL,6, Juan Carlos has appeared in Madrid's   
OL,7, Puerta del Sol square.                 
OL,9,FHe is shown aiming a rifle at a larger 
OL,10,Fstatue of a bear, an emblem of Madrid. 
OL,12,FJuan Carlos, who abdicated in favour of
OL,13,Fhis son Felipe in 2014 after 39 years  
OL,14,Fon the throne, has been heavily        
OL,15,Fcriticised for his love of hunting.    
OL,17,FThe sculpture of the ex-king appeared  
OL,18,Fwithin hours of him leaving Spain after
OL,19,Fa brief visit from self-imposed exile  
OL,20,Fin the United Arab Emirates.           
